## 2 · Code Quality & Maintenance
2.1 **Update > Duplicate** Improve existing logic; delete deprecated versions.  
2.2 **No Dead Code** Call it out in the summary and remove it.  
2.3 **Readable & Typed** Respect language conventions (PEP‑8 + type hints, TS strict, etc.).  
2.4 **Self‑Documenting** Keep comments/doc‑strings current; remove stale docs.  
2.5 **Library Policy** Prefer current deps; add new ones only if well‑maintained *and* truly needed.  

