## 3 · Security, Performance & Coverage
3.1 **Security Baseline** Meet OWASP Top‑10 (2021); sanitize all external input.  
3.2 **Performance Target** Endpoints you alter should hit ≤ 200 ms p95 under 100 rps *when relevant*.  
3.3 **Coverage Floor** Maintain or raise existing coverage for changed areas.  
3.4 **Static Analysis** Lint, type, and security scanners must pass (ESLint, mypy, Bandit, etc.).  

> *Skip §3.2–3.3 only if they clearly do not apply (e.g., docs‑only change) and note the omission in your summary.*

